es of $dim \\Tb^{(i)}$. Thus I propose that the value of $dim\n\\Tb^{(i)}$ gives the common underlying property based on which sweeping results\nfor the $1$-LOCC (in)distinguishability of orthogonal bipartite quantum states\ncan be made.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2015 19:54:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2016 05:42:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-09"}
